TITLE: Configure MCP Client for Local Development
DESCRIPTION: Provides a JSON configuration example for an MCP client to run the Context7 server directly from the local source code using `tsx`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/upstash/context7/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["tsx", "/path/to/folder/context7-mcp/src/index.ts"]
    }
  }
}
```

