TITLE: Configure Context7 MCP in Cursor (Deno) - JSON
DESCRIPTION: Configures the Context7 MCP server in Cursor using Deno as the runtime. This configuration runs the package directly from npm via Deno's compatibility layer, requiring network and environment permissions. Requires Deno installed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/upstash/context7/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {
      "command": "deno",
      "args": ["run", "--allow-env", "--allow-net", "npm:@upstash/context7-mcp"]
    }
  }
}
```

----------------------------------------

