----------------------------------------

TITLE: Configure MCP Inspector with experimental VM modules (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: JSON configuration snippet for MCP Inspector to run the Context7 MCP server with the `--experimental-vm-modules` Node.js flag via `npx`, addressing potential ESM resolution issues.
SOURCE: https://github.com/upstash/context7/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": [
        "-y",
        "--node-options=--experimental-vm-modules",
        "@upstash/context7-mcp@1.0.6"
      ]
    }
  }
}

```

