TITLE: Install Context7 MCP in Claude Code
DESCRIPTION: Provides the shell command to add the Context7 MCP server configuration directly using the `claude mcp add` command.
SOURCE: https://github.com/upstash/context7/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
claude mcp add context7 -- npx -y @upstash/context7-mcp@latest
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Install Context7 MCP via Smithery - Bash
DESCRIPTION: Installs the Context7 MCP server using the Smithery CLI and npx, specifically targeting the Claude client. This command fetches and runs the latest version of the Context7 MCP package. Requires Node.js and the Smithery CLI.
SOURCE: https://github.com/upstash/context7/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npx -y @smithery/cli install @upstash/context7-mcp --client claude
```

